Decret of bc Lordis of Consale aganis Thomas Drumbrek and his spouff for lawboryng of be landis of Fepernar ·

At Edinburght pa xiij day of Decembris pe ger oi 'Gode M.cccc.1.xxxv geris tha bordis of Consale · · · decretis and de- lyueris pat Thomas Drumbrek and Agnes his spouff has done wrang in pe lawboryng and manuryng of pe landis os Febemer beiangin to be bischoprik of Abardene aa wes cierly previt besor pc lerdis and ardania paim to devoide and rad be samyn toa reuerend fadir in Goda Wilghame eie& confirmate of Abcrdene and pat bai sall content and pay to be sada reuerend fadir pe malis and profitis of pe sade landis of twa geris bigane as he may prusa befor be schareff of be scbyr bat pai are of vaila togidder with hyis costis and ikatbis bat he hes sustenyt par prow and ordanis our souerane lordis lettares be dere& to be schereff to tak pe sada preif befor him and to warne bc perty parto · and pe sade Thomas was lauchfully sommond to bis aaron and oft tymes cailit and nocht comperit · Extrattum de libro actorum per mc Alex- andrum Scot rectorem da Wigtone clericum rotulorum et registri ac confilij regis·
